17 technical education under section 15-20.1-24 or an individual who is provisionally
18 approved by the department of career and technical education under section
19 15-20.1-25 to serve as a career advisor.
20 5. The requirement under subsection 1 or 2 is met if the school district :
21 a. Actively recruited and attempted to hire the requisite number of qualified school
22 counselors or career advisors;
